Info.Title: The Mule
Info.Writer: Leigh Whannell, Angus Sampson, Jaime Browne, Jaime Browne (story)
Info.Actors: Hugo Weaving, Angus Sampson, Leigh Whannell, Ewen Leslie
Info.Plot: After a trip to Thailand, a first-time drug mule finds himself in police custody, with his stomach crammed with narcotics. Now, he has to endure seven sphincter-clenching days to convince them of his innocence. Will nature take its course?
